n\\n## Constraints & Preferences\\n- Tests must be Java under existing `src/test/java` tree.\\n- Modify only the test file unless build changes are strictly necessary.\\n- Use only public API; no direct reflection or serialization.\\n- Avoid deprecated APIs.\\n- Tests must run under Native Image by default.\\n- Do not skip Native Image execution.\\n- If behavior fundamentally requires open-ended dynamic class loading, catch `Error`, verify with `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(e)`, and rethrow otherwise.\\n- Do not compile or run tests manually; external workflow runs them.\\n- All top-level test classes must be public.\\n- Individual tests must complete under 60 seconds with bounded waits and resource cleanup.\\n- Local `tests/src/AGENTS.md`: test code should not use `GradleException`; `build.gradle` changes only in `graalvmNative` and only for `--add-opens`/`--add-exports`.\\n\\n## Progress\\n### Done\\n- [x] Replaced placeholder test in `tests/src/org.eclipse.jetty.ee10/jetty-ee10-webapp/12.0.10/src/test/java/org_eclipse_jetty_ee10/jetty_ee10_webapp/Jetty_ee10_webappTest.java`.\\n- [x] Added tests covering:\\n  - `WebAppContext` configuration lifecycle, resource aliases, servlet holder registration, and parsed descriptor metadata.\\n  - `WebDescriptor` and `FragmentDescriptor` parsing.\\n  - `MetaData` origins, override descriptors, web-inf/container resources, fragments, and `AbsoluteOrdering`.\\n  - `Configurations` sorting, lifecycle callbacks, protected/hidden classes, and removal.\\n  - `WebAppContext` mutable descriptor/resource/class matcher settings.\\n- [x] Removed `@TempDir` because `/tmp` was out of space in test runs; now uses `build/tmp/jetty-ee10-webapp-tests/...` with recursive cleanup.\\n- [x] Replaced deprecated `org.eclipse.jetty.ee10.webapp.ClassMatcher`/system/server matcher APIs with `org.eclipse.jetty.util.ClassMatcher` and protected/hidden matcher APIs.\\n- [x] Removed server startup with `Server`/`LocalConnector` after default